These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, collecting
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: satire, scientific
1. the person watching satire movies is in an even position##4
2. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | collecting | card-games |
| Movie-Genre     | scientific    | satire   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, soy-milk
2 different games are played: billiard, chess
1. the person playing billiard is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | coffee        |
| Game      | billiard  | chess |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: drama, superhero
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, turkish
1. the canadian is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero    | drama |
| Nationality   | canadian | turkish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, october
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, mango
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person eating mango is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Birthday   | august      | october |
| Food       | broccoli | mango    |

 #################################

 
