.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-12::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, jazz
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: bellflower, zinnia
1. the person who growsbellflower is the fan of disco##1
2. the person who growszinnia is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz       | disco   |
| Flower   | zinnia | bellflower |

